l. (Exp. Astron. 35, 391-412, 2013;\nAstrophys. J. Suppl. 212, 12, 2014). In this paper, we characterize the CsI(Tl)\nabsorbers coupled to SiPM. We also present the experimental results from the\nfully assembled configuration of the Compton polarimeter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Oct 2015 22:39:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-26"}
