er than solar of about 0.15/0.5 dex.\nThis testifies the presence of dust inside the medium, with a depletion factor\nof Iron of about 40%.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Oct 2015 10:21:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-26"}
